INFO 2025-04-20 07:02:51,457 doc_processor 30 140238363454336 Generating title and summary for text: Individualized Care & Engagement Plan for Karen

This care plan has been developed to ensure that Karen, receives the highest level of care
and  support  while  allowing  her  to  continue  living  comfortably  at  home  with  her  beloved
dog,  Casey.  As  her  cognitive  challenges  progresses  and  arthritis  affects  her  hand
coordination, this plan is designed to support her cognitive function, mobility, and personal
care while promoting independence and respecting her dignity.

Karen’s care has transitioned from 8-hour shifts to live-in support at your request to provide
more  consistent  supervision  and  assistance.  To  further  enhance  nighttime  safety,  an
