In cognizance of the Harmonized Client Satisfaction Measurement (CSM) and Anti-Red
Tape Authority Memorandum Circulars 2022-005 and 2023-005, all Responsibility Centers
providing internal and external services must record all received, completed, and
pending transactions. This data will be included in the Client Satisfaction Measurement Report
(CSMR) to be submitted by the University to the Anti-Red Tape Authority every last working day

of April, as required by Section 4.7 of the circular.

