SUBJECT:

Deadline for Submission of Approved Project Procurement
Management Plan (PPMP) for FY 2023

All Responsibility Centers (RCs) are to submit their respective approved Project
Procurement Management Plans (PPMPs) FY 2023 for GAA (Fund 01), Income (Fund 05), and
Fiduciary (Fund 05) to the Procurement Management Division (PMD) on or before October 14,
2022 for consolidation into the Annual Procurement Plan (APP). PPMPs submitted late will not
be included in the APP.

PPMPs shall strictly conform to the following:

•  PPMPs shall be generated by accessing the online form, saved in the system and

