RESOLVED,  that  upon  the  recommendation  of  the  President  of  the

University and the Executive Committee of the Board of Regents, the proposal to

convert in the database History 003 (History of Filipino Muslims and Indigenous

Peoples  of  MINSUPALA)  as  GEC  110,  Filipino  101  (Wika  at  Kultura  sa

